{"tid":253241,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"3DS的Sighax被放出，3DS最後一塊拼圖完成","createTime":"2017-05-22T08:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T14:04:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e724ab39ee724149efcaf9e67e31a0280f6b2bfd","tid":253241,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"2017/05/21 06:19<br />\n今天，開發者們放出了3DS的Sighax，雖然早在2016年12月的33C3研討會上，Sighax就已經被公開，但是直到今天才正式被放出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSighax是什麼？<br />\nSighax是3DS的最底層硬件啓動芯片BootROM exploit. 因為任天堂對於RSA加密解析的不完善，開發者們通過某種特殊的暴力運算方法，取得了3DS最底層的密鑰。通過這個密鑰，可以對任何固件進行數字簽名，並且安裝到任何3ds/2ds/new 3ds上。即使是沒有安裝過自制固件的3DS，包括大陸/港台地區的3DS，不管是什麼系統版本包括最新的11.4的官方系統，都能通過Sighax刷寫自治系統。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為是利用獲取的密鑰對固件進行簽名，任何被簽名的固件都會被3DS識別成有效。Nintendo除非更換掉3DS本身的硬件芯片，沒有任何系統升級可以消除Sighax，這也是3DS最後的補完。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟A9LH的區別？<br />\nA9LH是在3DS的原系統加載時，通過修改過的Boot跳轉，進入自制系統。Sighax將機器本身的系統替換成自制系統，擁有比A9LH更底層的啓動權限。<br />\n<br />\nA9LH的開發者之一plutoo對此稱「Sighax是3DS的棺木上最後一顆釘子，3DS完美謝幕，我們下一台機器再見」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sighax.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sighax.com&d=OeNbSnhVY7UVR%2FdNhh%2F7B%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b9d33d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sighax.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://3ds.guide/updating-to-boot9strap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3ds.guide%2Fupdating-to-boot9strap&d=OeNbSnhVY7UVR%2FdNhh%2F7B%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=dccface0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://3ds.guide/updating-to-boot9strap</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hackinformer.com/2017/05/20/sighax-3ds-finally-released/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhackinformer.com%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2Fsighax-3ds-finally-released%2F&d=OeNbSnhVY7UVR%2FdNhh%2F7B%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f8dc0a70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hackinformer.com/2017/05/20/sighax-3ds-finally-released/</a>"},{"pid":"536002025b07b509d2cd89da1e11ed3b2744d77d","tid":253241,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c801c2f7536d5723c7af318226a3712c5ef970","tid":253241,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c251ffcfee5bd6a06099906618a3122fb1cbedc7","tid":253241,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b5d0aafec18c410ac3fa859a8b34a6205e5cde","tid":253241,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}